import {
  Helmet
} from 'react-helmet';
import React, {
  Fragment
} from 'react';


const Register = () => ( <
  Fragment >
  <
  Helmet > < title > Nimelssa quiz - Registeration page < /title></Helmet >
  <
  div className = "row" >
  <
  div className = "col s12 m4 offset-m4" >
  <
  div className = "card z-depth-4" >
  <
  div className = "card-content black white-text" >
  <
  span className = "card-title" > Craete Account < /span> <
  /div> <
  div className = "card-content" >

  <
  div className = "input-field" >
  <
  i className = "material-icons prefix" > account_circle < /i> <
  input id = "uid"
  type = "text" > < /input> <
  label htmlFor = "uid" > User Name < /label> <
  /div>

  <
  div className = "input-field" >
  <
  i className = "material-icons prefix" > edit < /i> <
  input id = "matric"
  type = "number" > < /input> <
  label htmlFor = "matric" > Matric Number < /label> <
  /div>

  <
  div className = "input-field" >
  <
  i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
  input id = "password"
  type = "password" > < /input> <
  label htmlFor = "password" > Password < /label> <
  /div>

  <
  div className = "input-field" >
  <
  i className = "material-icons prefix" > account_box < /i> <
  input id = "role"
  type = "text" > < /input> <
  label htmlFor = "role" > Role < /label> <
  /div>

  <
  div >
  <
  label >
  &
  nbsp; < input id = "indeterminate-checkbox"
  type = "checkbox" / >
  <
  span > Do you approve the above deatils < /span> <
  /label> <
  /div><br / >

  <
  div >
  <
  label >
  &
  nbsp; < button style = {
    {
      width: 100
    }
  }
  className = "waves-effect waves-light btn blue" > Register < /button> <
  /label> <
  /div><br / >

  <
  /div> <
  /div> <
  /div> <
  /div> <
  /Fragment>
)

export default Register;
